<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The following are some frequently asked questions about installing and using ITOM Container Deployment Foundation (CDF).</p><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 500; margin: 25px 0px 6px; overflow: hidden; padding-top: 0em; padding-bottom: 0.17em; border-bottom: none; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(0, 115, 231) !important; font-size: 24px !important;"><span id="What_are_the_recommended_deployment_modes_for_CDF?" style="box-sizing: border-box;"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="What_are_the_recommended_deployment_modes_for_CDF.3F" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span id="What_are_the_recommended_deployment_modes_for_CDF.3F" style="box-sizing: border-box;"></span><span id="What_are_the_recommended_deployment_modes_for_CDF.3F" class="mw-headline" style="box-sizing: border-box;">What are the recommended deployment modes for CDF?</span></span></h2><ul style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.3em 0px 0px 1.6em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0.1em;">One master node, at least three worker nodes, and a separate NFS server.</li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0.1em;">Multiple master nodes, at least three worker nodes, and a separate NFS server.</li></ul><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 500; margin: 25px 0px 6px; overflow: hidden; padding-top: 0em; padding-bottom: 0.17em; border-bottom: none; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(0, 115, 231) !important; font-size: 24px !important;"><span id="Can_I_upgrade_the_suite_images_in_CDF?" style="box-sizing: border-box;"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Can_I_upgrade_the_suite_images_in_CDF.3F" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span id="Can_I_upgrade_the_suite_images_in_CDF.3F" style="box-sizing: border-box;"></span><span id="Can_I_upgrade_the_suite_images_in_CDF.3F" class="mw-headline" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Can I upgrade the suite images in CDF?</span></span></h2><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">You will need to log in the management portal, click&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">SUITE &gt;&nbsp;<span class="image" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a href="https://docs.microfocus.com/mediawiki/index.php?title=Special:Upload&amp;wpDestFile=https://docs.microfocus.com/mediawiki/images/f/fb/2018.04/attachments/17859066/22185968.png" class="new" title="File:https://docs.microfocus.com/mediawiki/images/f/fb/2018.04/attachments/17859066/22185968.png" style="box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(165, 88, 88); background: none transparent;">22185968.png</a></span>&nbsp;&gt; Update</span>&nbsp;to upgrade suite.</p><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 500; margin: 25px 0px 6px; overflow: hidden; padding-top: 0em; padding-bottom: 0.17em; border-bottom: none; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(0, 115, 231) !important; font-size: 24px !important;"><span id="Will_the_logs_located_in_a_pod_be_deleted_when_the_pod_is_deleted?" style="box-sizing: border-box;"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Will_the_logs_located_in_a_pod_be_deleted_when_the_pod_is_deleted.3F" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span id="Will_the_logs_located_in_a_pod_be_deleted_when_the_pod_is_deleted.3F" style="box-sizing: border-box;"></span><span id="Will_the_logs_located_in_a_pod_be_deleted_when_the_pod_is_deleted.3F" class="mw-headline" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Will the logs located in a pod be deleted when the pod is deleted?</span></span></h2><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">All the suite logs are currently stored within the persistent volume, so you will not lose them if the pods go down. This applies to both on-premise and cloud-based deployments.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span id="How_do_I_restart_the_CDF_cluster_.28foundation_components.29.3F" class="mw-headline" style="box-sizing: border-box;">How do I restart the CDF cluster (foundation components)?</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Run the following commands to restart the CDF cluster:</p><pre style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 240); padding: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 1.25em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; overflow: auto;">cd ${K8S_HOME}/bin
./kube-restart.sh</pre><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span id="Do_I_need_to_add_exceptions_to_the_firewall_policy.3F" style="box-sizing: border-box;"></span><span id="Do_I_need_to_add_exceptions_to_the_firewall_policy.3F" class="mw-headline" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Do I need to add exceptions to the firewall policy?</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Browsers access CDF via HTTPS ports (TCP/5443). End users need to add it to the firewall exception policy.</p>